{"tid":1040776,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"陳茂波表示不會再透過「關愛共享」計劃派錢","createTime":"2019-02-28T10:30:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-28T12:32:55.000Z","uid":36901,"like":2,"dislike":31,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"6e96d2e89b70f575f9af2397ca2d5531cddb0da8","tid":1040776,"uid":36901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T10:30:57.000Z","msg":"陳茂波表示不會再透過「關愛共享」計劃派錢<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n財政司司長陳茂波出席立法會財委會解釋新一份財政預算案。民主黨胡志偉不滿政府為何不向已經填寫申領4000元「關愛共享」計劃的市民，再發放3000元，有關做法不需額外行政費。<br />\n<br />\n陳茂波說，事情並非如此簡單，因為市民的年齡、退稅和差餉情況都與去年不同，如果只是簡單以原有的填表資料作準則，便會引起不公平、不滿意、不開心，只會添煩添亂，因此目前不會再透過「關愛共享」計劃派錢。<br />\n<br />\n人民力量陳志全關注政府會否全民派錢，陳茂波說，全民派錢並不符合本屆政府的理財新哲學。<br />\n<br />\n個system徙撚左咁多行政費,你話俾我聽只用一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db76fad9ee2550caa1142e0c46c5a75a5dabca5a","tid":1040776,"uid":1550,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T10:45:50.000Z","msg":"佢有system咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4a7c401151c3a704f9c916ea489f2881e5d434b","tid":1040776,"uid":41818,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T10:52:17.000Z","msg":"理財新哲學"},{"pid":"13560342041f1dd23ba3b0d231a8be68db851400","tid":1040776,"uid":36901,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"quote":{"pid":"f4a7c401151c3a704f9c916ea489f2881e5d434b","tid":1040776,"uid":41818,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T10:52:17.000Z","msg":"理財新哲學"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T10:57:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />點解唔全民派<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />因為人人有唔公平<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁關愛共享得喇掛<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />因為唔係人人有所以唔公平<br />\n<br />\n呢個就係理財新哲學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" c